title: The Crusades with Dan Jones
itunes:title: The Crusades with Dan Jones
itunes:subtitle: The two Dans are back. And this time, they're talking all things crusades. In this rerun episode, Dan Jones provides his namesake host with a thrilling background to the series of holy wars that have come to define Medieval Europe.
